{"tid":626126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍塘月台助理確診腦膜炎雙球菌！","createTime":"2018-04-12T01:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T04:27:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a9992f1210961695ab267c40dcb419a0f538e6d7","tid":626126,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"港鐵今日凌晨發出通告，表示昨日接獲衞生防護中心通知，一名九龍塘站工作的月台助理，確診感染腦膜炎雙球菌，港鐵緊急安排九龍塘站，以一比四十九濃度的漂白水進行清潔消毒。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，與衞生防護中心保持緊密聯繫，並即時按照衞生防護中心指引制訂的既定程序，為九龍塘站進行清潔消毒，及加強清洗通風隔塵網，並要求車站員工若出現發燒、咳嗽等病徵，應盡快求診醫治，並知會上司。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180412/_2018041207462198179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180412%2F_2018041207462198179.jpg&h=94e2a0e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1188054/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1188054%2F&d=Pwj1qcM7NItuKhpa9TTTipUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=2f582f56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1188054%2F&h=1675420a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1188054/</a></div>"},{"pid":"e4b85702b498c42cf6482b8f75f0b9da1cd3d398","tid":626126,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:37:19.000Z","msg":"腦膜炎雙球菌感染傳播途徑，主要經由患者咳嗽或打噴嚏而產生的飛沫或直接接觸患者呼吸道分泌物而傳播。潛伏期由 2 － 10 天，一般為 3 － 4 天。當細菌入侵血液或包圍腦部及脊髓的內膜（流行性腦膜炎）時，可引致嚴重病症。腦膜炎雙球菌血症的病徵包括突發性發燒、劇烈頭痛、皮膚出現瘀斑、休克，而嚴重者甚至會致命。流行性腦膜炎的病徵包括發高燒、劇烈頭痛、頸部僵硬及嗜睡，亦會有嘔吐、畏光或皮疹等情況出現，若情況嚴重更可造成腦部損害或死亡。腦部損害可導致智力受影響、智力發展遲緩、失聰及電解質失衡。侵入性腦膜炎雙球菌感染更可引致關節炎、心肌炎、眼內炎或肺炎。"},{"pid":"728a0b2d453d8f5518794fcb6ab31e67c04b288a","tid":626126,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:38:45.000Z","msg":"午餐肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173327b495dc6175a45fb424df5c121e976ce633","tid":626126,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:39:05.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n都係要返工"},{"pid":"adec244956e067c9ceeb2c9ad8c2d115aacff532","tid":626126,"uid":66395,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:43:34.000Z","msg":"返垃圾工返到中d 咁危險既病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ae3632765add150da43076046c83e86c861094","tid":626126,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:45:15.000Z","msg":"多識黨？"},{"pid":"382282e388d26b06c8882c9292053110cbb4e217","tid":626126,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"炒散嚟？"},{"pid":"c1b99b805cf5ea6f93a3a5f3babe02e7b7606493","tid":626126,"uid":156005,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日都經係咪死撚硬"},{"pid":"26146c326e363d44306a1dc2f91c5c77b31a8cd8","tid":626126,"uid":123790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adec244956e067c9ceeb2c9ad8c2d115aacff532","tid":626126,"uid":66395,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:43:34.000Z","msg":"返垃圾工返到中d 咁危險既病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:38:04.000Z","msg":"番垃圾工都要搵命搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df53eef6a34901eeabeaed929cfd76e98130ac17","tid":626126,"uid":98386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:45:30.000Z","msg":"班支那狗同廢中廢老最鍾意就係放聲大咳 日日索埋索埋咁多唔中招就有鬼啦"},{"pid":"b8134263ea7751bc13725038a7b254d6cd11d2c3","tid":626126,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26146c326e363d44306a1dc2f91c5c77b31a8cd8","tid":626126,"uid":123790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adec244956e067c9ceeb2c9ad8c2d115aacff532","